name: SoundsofDwyer
0:
”Alexa, open sounds of dwyer”
”Alexa, ask sounds of dwyer to give me some inspiration”
”Alexa, ask sounds of dwyer to play a few quotes”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sounds of dwyer
des:
Ever miss hearing Andy Dwyer's voice? Alexa will bring it to you with this skill. New quotes added regularly!

Get your daily dose of Andy Dwyer inspiration.

Latest update: 
- Alexa will keep playing clips if you ask her for a 'few quotes' or 'some pieces of wisdom'. Otherwise she will just play one quote.
- Improved audio trimming and loudness. 
- Improved randomization when playing several quotes in a row.
(Improved randomization for single quotes will be in a future update)

Have a quote you'd like to hear that isn't there yet? Contact me to get it published!
